msgctxt "MediationAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"One or multiple predictor variables predicting the mediators and the outcome "
"variables."
msgstr "一個或多個預測變項預測中介變項與結果變項。"

msgctxt "MediationAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Variables through which the indirect effect of the predictors on the "
"outcomes is hypothesized to flow."
msgstr "假設預測變項對結果變項之間接效果會經由其傳遞的變項。"

