msgid "Standardize based on latent variable variances only."
msgstr "僅根據潛在變項的變異數進行標準化。"

msgctxt "MediationAnalysis|"
msgid "Standardize excluding exogenous covariates."
msgstr "不包含外生共變項的標準化。"

