msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Define latent factors and assign observed indicator variables to each factor."
msgstr "定義潛在因素並將觀察指標變項指派至各因素。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Specify moderator variables and their effects on measurement model "
"parameters."
msgstr "指定調節變項及其對測量模型參數之影響。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Variables hypothesized to moderate the measurement model parameters. "
"Continuous moderators can optionally include squared and cubic effects."
msgstr "假設會調節測量模型參數之變項。連續型調節變項可選擇納入平方與立方效果。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Include a quadratic (squared) effect for this moderator."
msgstr "為此調節變項納入二次（平方）效果。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Include a cubic effect for this moderator."
msgstr "為此調節變項納入三次（立方）效果。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Click to start or synchronize the analysis. The analysis does not run "
"automatically due to computational intensity."
msgstr "點按以開始或同步分析。由於計算量較大，分析不會自動執行。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Check measurement invariance assumptions by testing model fit across groups "
"defined by the moderator variables."
msgstr "透過檢定調節變項所定義之各群組的模型適配度，以檢驗測量不變性假設。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Fit the measurement model separately in each group to verify that the model "
"fits adequately before testing moderation."
msgstr "在檢定調節效果前，先分別於各群組中配適測量模型，以確認模型適配度良好。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Number of groups into which continuous moderator variables are split for the "
"assumption check."
msgstr "為進行假設檢驗而將連續型調節變項分割成的群組數。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Save the group variable created by splitting the continuous moderator to the "
"dataset."
msgstr "將分割連續型調節變項所產生之群組變項儲存至資料集。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Include interaction terms between pairs of moderators."
msgstr "納入成對調節變項之間的交互作用項。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Configure invariance test levels and specify which individual parameters "
"should be tested for moderation."
msgstr "設定不變性檢定層級，並指定哪些個別參數應進行調節效果檢驗。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Select the levels of measurement invariance to test. Each level constrains "
"an additional set of parameters to be equal across moderator values."
msgstr ""
"選擇要檢驗的測量不變性層級。每個層級會將額外一組參數限制為在調節變項各數值間"
"相等。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Test configural invariance: same factor structure across groups but all "
"parameters free."
msgstr "檢驗組態不變性：各群組因素結構相同，但所有參數自由估計。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Test metric invariance: constrain factor loadings to be equal across groups."
msgstr "檢驗度量不變性：限制各群組之因素負荷量相等。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Test scalar invariance: constrain factor loadings and intercepts to be equal "
"across groups."
msgstr "檢驗純量不變性：限制各群組之因素負荷量與截距相等。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Test strict invariance: constrain factor loadings, intercepts, and residual "
"variances to be equal across groups."
msgstr "檢驗嚴格不變性：限制各群組之因素負荷量、截距與殘差變異數相等。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Define a custom set of parameter constraints for invariance testing."
msgstr "為不變性檢定定義自訂的參數限制組合。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"For each invariance level, specify which individual measurement parameters "
"should be tested for moderation effects."
msgstr "對於每個不變性層級，指定應檢驗調節效果之個別測量參數。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Estimation Options"
msgstr "估計選項"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Indicator preprocessing"
msgstr "指標前處理"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "None"
msgstr "無"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Center"
msgstr "平減（中心化）"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Z-standardize"
msgstr "Z 標準化"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Select additional output tables and parameter estimates to display."
msgstr "選擇要顯示的額外輸出表格與參數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Select which measurement model parameter estimates to display in the output."
msgstr "選擇要在輸出中顯示的測量模型參數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Significance level for flagging parameter estimates."
msgstr "標記參數估計值之顯著水準。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display factor loading estimates."
msgstr "顯示因素負荷量估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display intercept estimates for observed indicators."
msgstr "顯示觀察指標之截距估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display residual variance estimates for observed indicators."
msgstr "顯示觀察指標之殘差變異數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display latent factor variance estimates."
msgstr "顯示潛在因素之變異數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display latent factor mean estimates."
msgstr "顯示潛在因素之平均數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Display latent factor covariance estimates."
msgstr "顯示潛在因素之共變數估計值。"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid "Show warnings"
msgstr "顯示警告"

msgctxt "ModeratedNonLinearFactorAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Configure marginal effects plots showing how measurement parameters change "
"as a function of the moderator variables."
msgstr "設定邊際效果圖，呈現測量參數隨調節變項變化之情形。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Specify the PLS-SEM model using cSEM syntax. Define measurement models (e."
"g., 'eta1 =~ y1 + y2 + y3') and structural model (e.g., 'eta2 ~ eta1')."
msgstr ""
"使用cSEM語法指定PLS-SEM模型。定義測量模型（例如「eta1 =~ y1 + y2 + y3」）與結"
"構模型（例如「eta2 ~ eta1」）。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Model-level settings such as grouping variables for multi-group analysis."
msgstr "模型層級之設定，例如多群組分析之分組變項。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Select a grouping variable to perform multi-group PLS-SEM analysis."
msgstr "選擇分組變項以執行多群組PLS-SEM分析。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Settings for the PLS-SEM estimation algorithm, convergence criteria, and "
"error calculation."
msgstr "PLS-SEM估計演算法、收斂標準與誤差計算之設定。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Use consistent PLS (PLSc) to correct for attenuation, producing consistent "
"estimates for common factor models."
msgstr "使用一致PLS（PLSc）進行衰減校正，以產生共同因素模型之一致估計。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Choose the scheme for estimating inner weights relating constructs to each "
"other."
msgstr "選擇用於估計構念間關係之內部權重方案。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Estimate the measurement model only, ignoring the structural (inner) model."
msgstr "僅估計測量模型，忽略結構（內部）模型。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Criterion used to assess convergence of the PLS algorithm."
msgstr "用於評估PLS演算法收斂性之準則。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Tolerance threshold for the convergence criterion. Smaller values require "
"stricter convergence."
msgstr "收斂準則之容許門檻值。數值愈小表示收斂要求愈嚴格。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Method for computing standard errors and confidence intervals."
msgstr "計算標準誤與信賴區間之方法。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Select the error calculation method."
msgstr "選擇誤差計算方法。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Do not compute standard errors or confidence intervals."
msgstr "不計算標準誤與信賴區間。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Compute standard errors and confidence intervals using bootstrap resampling."
msgstr "使用拔靴法重抽樣計算標準誤與信賴區間。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Number of bootstrap resamples to draw."
msgstr "拔靴法重抽樣之次數。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Width of the bootstrap confidence intervals."
msgstr "拔靴法信賴區間之寬度。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"How to handle bootstrap samples that produce inadmissible results (e.g., "
"Heywood cases)."
msgstr "處理產生不當解（例如 Heywood 案例）之拔靴法樣本的方式。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Replace inadmissible bootstrap samples with new ones."
msgstr "以新的拔靴法樣本取代不當之樣本。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Keep inadmissible results in the bootstrap distribution."
msgstr "保留拔靴法分配中之不當結果。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Drop inadmissible bootstrap samples, reducing the effective number of "
"resamples."
msgstr "剔除不當之拔靴法樣本，因而減少有效重抽樣次數。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Additional output tables and statistics to display."
msgstr "要顯示的額外輸出表格與統計量。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Display the proportion of variance explained for each endogenous construct."
msgstr "顯示每個內生構念之解釋變異比例。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Display additional fit indices for evaluating model fit."
msgstr "顯示用於評估模型適配度之額外適配指標。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Display Mardia's multivariate skewness and kurtosis coefficients to assess "
"multivariate normality."
msgstr "顯示 Mardia 多變量偏度與峰度係數，以評估多變量常態性。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Display reliability measures for each construct (e.g., Cronbach's alpha, "
"composite reliability)."
msgstr "顯示每個構念之信度指標（例如 Cronbach's alpha、組合信度）。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Display the observed correlation matrix of the indicator variables."
msgstr "顯示觀察指標變項之相關矩陣。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Display the model-implied correlation matrix of the indicator variables."
msgstr "顯示模型隱含之觀察指標變項相關矩陣。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Display the observed correlation matrix of the constructs."
msgstr "顯示觀察之構念相關矩陣。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Display the model-implied correlation matrix of the constructs."
msgstr "顯示模型隱含之構念相關矩陣。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Perform an overall model fit test using bootstrap-based tests."
msgstr "使用基於拔靴法之檢定執行整體模型適配度檢驗。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Number of bootstrap samples for the overall model fit test."
msgstr "整體模型適配度檢定之拔靴法樣本數。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Significance level for the overall model fit test."
msgstr "整體模型適配度檢定之顯著水準。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Use a saturated structural model as a reference for the model fit test."
msgstr "使用飽和結構模型作為模型適配度檢定之參考。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Save estimated construct scores as new columns in the dataset."
msgstr "將估計之構念分數儲存為資料集中的新欄位。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Settings for cross-validated prediction of endogenous indicator scores."
msgstr "內生指標分數之交叉驗證預測設定。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Perform k-fold cross-validation to predict endogenous indicator scores."
msgstr "執行 k 折交叉驗證以預測內生指標分數。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Number of folds for cross-validation. Higher values increase computation "
"time but reduce bias."
msgstr "交叉驗證之折數。數值愈高會增加計算時間，但可減少偏誤。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Number of times the cross-validation is repeated to reduce variance in the "
"prediction metrics."
msgstr "為減少預測指標之變異而重複交叉驗證的次數。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid ""
"Select a benchmark model to compare the prediction accuracy of the PLS-SEM "
"model."
msgstr "選擇基準模型以比較 PLS-SEM 模型之預測精確度。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "No benchmark comparison."
msgstr "不進行基準模型比較。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Compare against a linear regression model."
msgstr "與線性迴歸模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Compare against Generalized Structured Component Analysis."
msgstr "與廣義結構成分分析 (GSCA) 進行比較。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Compare against Principal Component Analysis."
msgstr "與主成份分析進行比較。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Compare against the MAXVAR approach."
msgstr "與 MAXVAR 方法進行比較。"

msgctxt "PLSSEM|"
msgid "Compare against all available benchmark models."
msgstr "與所有可用之基準模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Specify the structural equation model using lavaan syntax. Multiple models "
"can be specified and compared. See lavaan.org for syntax tutorials."
msgstr ""
"使用 lavaan 語法指定結構方程模型。可指定多個模型並進行比較。語法教學請參閱 "
"lavaan.org。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Enter the lavaan model syntax using variable names from the dataset."
msgstr "使用資料集中的變項名稱輸入 lavaan 模型語法。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Select whether the input is a raw data matrix or a variance-covariance "
"matrix."
msgstr "選擇輸入內容為原始資料矩陣或變異數－共變數矩陣。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Use raw data with observations as rows and variables in columns."
msgstr "使用原始資料，以觀察體為列（橫列）、變項為行（直行）。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Use a variance-covariance matrix as input. Requires specifying the sample "
"size."
msgstr "使用變異數－共變數矩陣作為輸入。需指定樣本數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "The number of observations the covariance matrix is based on."
msgstr "該共變數矩陣所依據之觀察體數目（樣本數）。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Select a variable from the dataset to use as sampling weights for each "
"observation."
msgstr "從資料集中選擇一個變項作為每個觀察體之抽樣權重。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Options for configuring the structural equation model specification."
msgstr "結構方程模型設定的選項。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"How the metric of latent variables is determined: by fixing the first "
"loading to 1 (Factor loadings), fixing factor variance to 1 (Factor "
"variance), fixing average loadings to 1 (Effects coding), or none."
msgstr ""
"潛在變項量尺之決定方式：將第一個負荷量設為 1（因素負荷量）、將因素變異數設為 "
"1（因素變異數）、將平均負荷量設為 1（效果編碼），或無。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Estimate observed intercepts and/or latent means. Some elements need to be "
"fixed for identification."
msgstr "估計觀察截距及／或潛在平均數。為達辨識，部分元素需設為固定值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Fix latent means to zero; observed intercepts are estimated freely."
msgstr "將潛在平均數固定為零；觀察截距則自由估計。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Fix observed intercepts to zero; latent means are estimated freely."
msgstr "將觀察截距固定為零；潛在平均數則自由估計。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Fix the mean of manifest intercepts to zero; latent means are estimated "
"freely."
msgstr "將觀察變項截距之平均數固定為0；潛在變項平均數自由估計。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Estimate factors as orthogonal (uncorrelated) instead of allowing them to "
"correlate."
msgstr "將因子設定為正交（不相關），而非允許其相關。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"If checked, exogenous covariates are considered fixed and their means, "
"variances, and covariances are fixed to sample values."
msgstr "若勾選，則外生共變量視為固定，其平均數、變異數與共變數將固定為樣本值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Condition on the exogenous covariates when estimating the model."
msgstr "在估計模型時，以外生共變量為條件。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Set the residual variance of a single indicator to zero if it is the only "
"indicator of a latent variable."
msgstr "若某單一指標為某潛在變項之唯一指標，則將其殘差變異數設為零。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Include residual variances of observed and latent variables as free "
"parameters."
msgstr "將觀察變項與潛在變項之殘差變異數納入為自由參數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Include covariances of exogenous latent variables in the model."
msgstr "將外生潛在變項之共變數納入模型中。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Include covariances of dependent variables (observed and latent) in the "
"model."
msgstr "將依變項（觀察變項與潛在變項）之共變數納入模型中。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Include thresholds for limited (non-continuous) dependent variables."
msgstr "納入有限（非連續）依變項之閾限。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Include response scaling parameters for limited (non-continuous) dependent "
"variables."
msgstr "納入有限（非連續）依變項之反應尺度參數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Impose constraints to make exploratory factor analysis blocks identifiable: "
"factor variances set to 1, covariances to zero, and loadings follow an "
"echelon pattern."
msgstr ""
"施加約束以達成探索性因素分析區塊之可辨識性：因素變異數設為 1，共變數設為零，"
"且因素負荷量採階梯模式。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Options for the estimation method, model test, standard errors, confidence "
"intervals, and missing data handling."
msgstr "估計方法、模型檢定、標準誤、信賴區間與遺漏值處理之選項。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Choose the estimation method. Some estimators set implicit options for test "
"and standard errors. ML-based extensions: MLM (robust SE, Satorra-Bentler "
"test), MLMV (robust SE, scaled-shifted test), MLMVS (robust SE, "
"Satterthwaite test), MLF (first-order SE), MLR (Huber-White SE, Yuan-Bentler "
"test). WLS variants: WLSM/WLSMV imply DWLS with robust SE, ULSM/ULSMV imply "
"ULS with robust SE."
msgstr ""
"選擇估計方法。部分估計量會隱含設定檢定與標準誤之選項。基於 ML 之擴展：MLM（強"
"韌標準誤、Satorra-Bentler 檢定）、MLMV（強韌標準誤、尺度平移檢定）、MLMVS（強"
"韌標準誤、Satterthwaite 檢定）、MLF（一階標準誤）、MLR（Huber-White 標準誤、"
"Yuan-Bentler 檢定）。WLS 變體：WLSM / WLSMV 隱含 DWLS 搭配強韌標準誤，ULSM / "
"ULSMV 隱含 ULS 搭配強韌標準誤。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Choose the test statistic for evaluating model fit. If left at Default, the "
"test is determined by the chosen estimator."
msgstr ""
"選擇用於評估模型適配度之檢定統計量。若保留為「預設」，則檢定方式由所選估計量"
"決定。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Number of bootstrap samples for the Bollen-Stine bootstrap test."
msgstr "Bollen-Stine 拔靴法檢定之拔靴法樣本數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Matrix used to compute the standard errors: expected, observed, or first "
"order (outer product of casewise scores)."
msgstr "用於計算標準誤之矩陣：期望資訊矩陣、觀察資訊矩陣，或一階（個案分數之外積）。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Method for computing standard errors. Standard uses the information matrix, "
"Robust uses robust.sem, Robust Huber-White uses the mlr approach, and "
"Bootstrap computes SEs from bootstrapped fits."
msgstr ""
"計算標準誤之方法。「標準」使用資訊矩陣，「強韌」使用 robust.sem，「強韌 "
"Huber-White」使用 mlr 途徑，「拔靴法」則從拔靴配適結果計算標準誤。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Number of bootstrap samples to use for computing standard errors."
msgstr "用於計算標準誤之拔靴法樣本數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Type of bootstrap confidence interval."
msgstr "拔靴法信賴區間之類型。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Width of the confidence intervals for parameter estimates."
msgstr "參數估計值之信賴區間寬度。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Set a seed to guarantee reproducible bootstrap results."
msgstr "設定種子數以確保拔靴法結果可重現。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Z-standardize all variables before estimation."
msgstr "在估計前將所有變項進行 Z 標準化。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"How to treat missing values. FIML uses full-information maximum likelihood. "
"Pairwise computes correlations using available pairs. Two-stage uses EM-"
"estimated statistics. Robust two-stage adds robustness against non-"
"normality. Doubly robust is for PML estimation."
msgstr ""
"遺漏值之處理方式。FIML 使用完全資訊最大概似法。Pairwise 使用可用配對計算相關"
"。Two-stage 使用 EM 估計之統計量。Robust two-stage 加入對抗非常態性之強韌性。"
"Doubly robust 適用於 PML 估計。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Emulate the output from different SEM programs."
msgstr "模擬不同 SEM 軟體之輸出格式。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Options for additional fit measures, parameter estimates, covariance "
"matrices, plots, and modification indices."
msgstr "額外適配指標、參數估計值、共變數矩陣、圖形與修正指標之選項。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display a table with various fit measures including CFI, TLI, RMSEA, SRMR, "
"and information criteria."
msgstr "顯示包含 CFI、TLI、RMSEA、SRMR 與資訊準則等多種適配指標之表格。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display the explained variance in each dependent variable."
msgstr "顯示每個依變項之解釋變異量。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display the amount of variance captured by a construct relative to "
"measurement error. Used to evaluate convergent validity."
msgstr "顯示構念相對於測量誤差所捕獲之變異量，用於評估收斂效度。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display the HTMT ratio to assess discriminant validity between constructs."
msgstr "顯示 HTMT 比值以評估構念間之區別效度。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display reliability metrics such as coefficient alpha and composite (omega) "
"reliability per latent variable."
msgstr "顯示每個潛在變項之信度指標，例如 alpha 係數與組合（omega）信度。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display Mardia's multivariate skewness and kurtosis coefficients to assess "
"multivariate normality."
msgstr "顯示 Mardia 多變量偏度與峰度係數，以評估多變量常態性。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display the observed covariance matrix calculated from the data."
msgstr "顯示由資料計算所得之觀察共變數矩陣。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display the model-implied covariance matrix based on estimated parameters."
msgstr "顯示基於估計參數之模型隱含共變數矩陣。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display residual covariances (observed minus implied)."
msgstr "顯示殘差共變數（觀察減去隱含）。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display the standardized residual covariance matrix."
msgstr "顯示標準化殘差共變數矩陣。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display standardized parameter estimates."
msgstr "顯示標準化參數估計值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Type of standardization."
msgstr "標準化之類型。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Standardize based on variances of both observed and latent variables."
msgstr "根據觀察變項與潛在變項的變異數進行標準化。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Standardize based on latent variable variances only."
msgstr "僅根據潛在變項的變異數進行標準化。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Standardize based on variances of observed and latent variables, excluding "
"exogenous covariates."
msgstr "基於觀察變項與潛在變項之變異數進行標準化，排除外生共變量。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display a path diagram of the model."
msgstr "顯示模型之路徑圖。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display parameter estimates on the path diagram."
msgstr "在路徑圖上顯示參數估計值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Show standardized estimates on the path diagram."
msgstr "在路徑圖上顯示標準化估計值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display a legend in the path diagram."
msgstr "在路徑圖中顯示圖例。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Display modification indices showing potential improvements to the model."
msgstr "顯示修正指標，呈現模型可能之改進方向。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Hide modification indices below the specified threshold."
msgstr "隱藏低於指定門檻值之修正指標。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Minimum value for modification indices to be displayed."
msgstr "修正指標顯示之最小值。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Display warnings produced by lavaan during estimation."
msgstr "顯示 lavaan 在估計過程中所產生之警告訊息。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Options for fitting the model across multiple groups, with equality "
"constraints on parameters."
msgstr "跨多群組配適模型之選項，並可對參數施加相等性限制。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Select a nominal or ordinal variable to fit the model separately for each "
"group."
msgstr "選擇一個名義或次序變項，以分別對每個群組配適模型。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain selected parameters to be equal across all groups."
msgstr "將選定之參數限制為所有群組皆相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain factor loadings to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將因素負荷量限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain intercepts to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將截距限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain residual variances to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將殘差變異數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain residual covariances to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將殘差共變數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain means to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將平均數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain thresholds to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將閾限限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain regression coefficients to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將迴歸係數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain latent variable variances to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將潛在變項之變異數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Constrain latent variable covariances to be equal across groups."
msgstr "將潛在變項之共變數限制為跨群組相等。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Release specific equality constraints using lavaan syntax, e.g., 'f=~x2' to "
"release a single loading."
msgstr "使用 lavaan 語法釋放特定之相等性限制，例如以「f =~ x2」釋放單一負荷量之限制。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Conduct sensitivity analysis against a potential missing confounder using "
"phantom variables."
msgstr "使用虛擬變項對潛在遺漏之干擾變項進行敏感度分析。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Run a sensitivity analysis by adding phantom variables (latent variables "
"without indicators) to assess the robustness of the model."
msgstr "透過加入虛擬變項（無指標之潛在變項）執行敏感度分析，以評估模型之穩健性。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Algorithm for sampling phantom variables."
msgstr "虛擬變項之抽樣演算法。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Use ant colony optimization to find good paths through the parameter space."
msgstr "使用蟻群最佳化演算法搜尋參數空間中的良好路徑。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Number of artificial ants per iteration, each representing a potential "
"solution."
msgstr "每次迭代中代表潛在解之人工螞蟻數量。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Number of best solutions stored during optimization."
msgstr "最佳化過程中儲存之最佳解數量。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"If the change in the objective function is smaller than this threshold, the "
"algorithm has converged."
msgstr "若目標函數之變化量低於此門檻值，則演算法已收斂。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid ""
"Use tabu search, which maintains a list of recently visited solutions to "
"avoid local optima."
msgstr ""
"使用禁忌搜尋法，該方法會維護一個近期已拜訪過之解的清單，以避免落入局部最佳解"
"。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Objective function maximized during the optimization."
msgstr "最佳化過程中最大化之目標函數。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Significance level for the sensitivity analysis."
msgstr "敏感度分析之顯著水準。"

msgctxt "SEM|"
msgid "Maximum number of iterations for the optimization algorithm."
msgstr "最佳化演算法之最大迭代次數。"
